nodes.text: Tessek, Sim Aloo, Pagetti Rook… Kenner Action Names Sold Separately!

"Tessek, Sim Aloo, Pagetti Rook… Kenner Action Names Sold Separately!" is an article written by Tim Veekhoven and published through the Star Wars Blog on September 13, 2013. It examines several action figures produced by the toy company Kenner for its 1980s Star Wars toy line with particular attention to comparing the names given them by Kenner versus those given them by other sources in the Expanded Universe.
